  "remarks": "Mehrada Akhlaghi KETABACHI was listed pursuant to paragraph 12 of resolution 1737 (2006), as read with resolutions 1747, 1803 and 1929, as: a person involved in nuclear or ballistic missile activities. Head of SBIG, which is designated under resolution 1737 (2006) for its role in the ballistic missile programme. The Director Disqualification Sanction was imposed on 09/04/2025.",
